{
  "stem": "25381.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is it, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we came to the ghetto, they took away my mother from there, from us-- separate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was 44 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was very young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was with the sisters together in the room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we got up and just to go outside-- and excuse me, my expression-- we had so much lice on our body.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The skin was full of like little holes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we used to go outside and just, with the hand, just like that, shovel from our body the lice.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was on the straw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They never changed the straw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I didn't see my mother anymore since-- since the day beginning of 1942.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We didn't see her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Just the three sisters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were separated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because the middle-- so we don't know whether they killed her before or whether they killed her while the last day from the slaughter.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We couldn't see her, whether she was in a different block, different house, because they separated us completely.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Different-- the elderly people and us, they used to take.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We walked like two, three miles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the German and the Polish soldiers, they took us with the rifles and with guns and we went on the field and we worked.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I digged like the coal-- you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Three layers from the ground, I digged the coal, you know, to this and pour it on a wheelbarrow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I had to carry it real heavy all the way on the empty lot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It should dry out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So whatever the girls, whatever-- and the young men, too, but the girls were separated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the men, we saw them from a distance.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
